  "instructions": [
    "In a pot, bring water to a boil. Add custard powder and stir until fully dissolved.",
    "Add rice and garlic cloves. Stir well to combine all ingredients.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for about 20 minutes or until rice is cooked through.",
    "Gently fold in roasted carrots and julienned bell peppers.",
    "Stir gently to ensure everything is evenly mixed and heated through.",
    "Remove from heat and let cool slightly before serving."
